elt vertiefende Beiträge zu ökologischen, kulturellen und architekturtheoretischen Dimensionen des Umbaus in Architektur, Stadt und Landschaft, und dies mit Querverweisen zu anderen Disziplinen.  aUmBau has appeared since 1979 as an interdisciplinary journal published by the Austrian Society for Architecture. It examines architectural production in its multifaceted contexts and interrelationships. The current issue explores the theme of reconstruction from the perspectives of urban history and architectural theory.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aBuilding. 0aConstruction industry. 4aBaubestand. 4aBauen im Bestand. 4aStädtebau. 4aUMBAU. 4aUM_BAU. 4aÖGFA. 7aARCHITECTURE / Urban & Land Use Planning.2bisacsh1 aBretschneider, Betül, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCzech, Hermann, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGregotti, Vittorio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHuhs, Ulrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLamster, Jörg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPsenner, Angelika, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRusso, Manfred, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVass, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVitali, Paolo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÖsterreichische Gesellschaft für Architektur, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook packa